title: Himalayan baba may allegedly be former finance minister Subramaniam, claims source - The New Indian Express
content: Himalayan baba may allegedly be former finance minister Subramaniam, claims source  The New Indian Express
description: If Subramaniam is established as the Baba, then the serious charge of leaking sensitive information to an outsider would go away. This theory is also being pushed by the NSE board, sources said.
